----------------------------------------------------------------------
SCOPE OF THIS LICENSE WITHIN THIS REPOSITORY
----------------------------------------------------------------------

This CC BY 4.0 license applies to the *documentation* in this repository:
  - README.md
  - DISCLOSURE.md
  - EXEC_BRIEF.md
  - METHODOLOGY.md
  - RAW_KANI_RESULTS.md
  - RECOMMENDED_PATCH.md
  - baseline/README.md
  - tests/engine/README.md (if added)
  - tests/wrapper/README.md (if added)

The *test code* in tests/engine/ and tests/wrapper/ is intended to be
contributed back to the upstream repositories under their respective
licenses:
  - tests/engine/  -> intended for github.com/aeyakovenko/percolator,
                      whose Cargo.toml declares license = "Apache-2.0".
                      The test code in tests/engine/ is therefore made
                      available under the Apache License, Version 2.0.
  - tests/wrapper/ -> intended for github.com/aeyakovenko/percolator-prog,
                      which does not declare a license in Cargo.toml at
                      sha c447686. The test code in tests/wrapper/ is
                      made available under the same CC BY 4.0 license as
                      the documentation until the upstream license is
                      clarified by the maintainer; the maintainer is
                      welcome to relicense any of these files under the
                      upstream's preferred license upon adoption.

Verify upstream licenses before redistributing test code at scale.
